Hi,

my name is Federico, I'm a student and I attend the Aerospace Engineering's course at Politecnico di Milano.

From the creative point of view, this is what this site is all about, I consider myself a photographer. My other interest are computers and web design, cinema, music and literature.

I usually carry with me 2 things: a camera (this can be my iPhone or just any other camera) and a moleskine notebook.

As far as what I do.. Well it's very simple, I make stuff, during the last five years I've tried everything (almost): web radio stations, blogs, shorts (movies), photojournalism, programming, web design and so on, but in this website I want to concentrate my thoughts on photography.

My favorite motto is: "Think Different".

Sometimes this just means "see the world in a different way" other times this implies become totally crazy and change your mind.

 

Where you can find me:

 

Flickr (that's my main photo-gallery)

Krop (my portfolio on Krop)

Twitter (my random ideas/thoughts/whatever else I can publish... )
